# 📊 Task 5 – Global Superstore Dashboard (Streamlit)

## 🚀 Project Overview
This project is an interactive Business Intelligence dashboard built using Streamlit. It analyzes Global Superstore sales data and provides insights into sales, profit, regions, categories, and customers.

---

## 🌐 Live Dashboard
👉 https://identifying-dream-cigarette-valued.trycloudflare.com/

---

## 📌 Features
- 💰 Total Sales & Profit KPIs
- 🌍 Region-wise performance analysis
- 📦 Category-wise sales distribution
- 📈 Monthly Sales & Profit trends
- 🏆 Top Customers analysis
- 🎛 Interactive filters (Region, Category, Segment)

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- Python 🐍
- Streamlit 📊
- Pandas 📑
- Plotly 📈

---

## 📂 Dataset
Global Superstore Dataset (CSV)

---

## 🎯 Objective
To demonstrate data analysis, visualization, and business intelligence skills by building an interactive dashboard.

